'''史蒂芬·德羅薩'''（'''Stephen DeRosa'''，{{bd|1968年|6月10日}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]電視劇和[[劇場_(藝術)|劇場]]演員。他在[[HBO|HBO]]電視劇《[[酒私風雲|酒私風雲]]》中飾演[[埃迪·康托爾|埃迪·康托爾]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.atlanticcityweekly.com/arts_and_entertainment/stephen-derosa-eddie-cantor-in-boardwalk-empire/article_c38b0958-a61b-5d86-9c2b-aaeffabff64f.html |title = Stephen DeRosa: Eddie Cantor in 'Boardwalk Empire' |author = Jeff Schwachter |date = 2012-02-09 |publisher = Atlantic City Weekly |language = en |accessdate = 2016-11-04 |archive-date = 2016-10-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161026181003/http://www.atlanticcityweekly.com/arts_and_entertainment/stephen-derosa-eddie-cantor-in-boardwalk-empire/article_c38b0958-a61b-5d86-9c2b-aaeffabff64f.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 教育 ==
他曾在[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓哥倫比亞特區]]的[[喬治城大學|喬治城大學]]上學當本科生，並於1995年畢業於[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]][[紐黑文|紐黑文]]的{{link-en|耶魯大學戲劇學院|Yale School of Drama}}，獲得[[藝術創作碩士|藝術創作碩士]]。

== 生涯 ==
儘管德羅薩的職業生涯主要集中在劇場，但他也曾在幾部電視節目中演出。

他在Playwrights Horizons劇場的The Acting Company舞台劇《''You Can't Take It With You''》中與[[F·莫瑞·亞伯拉罕|F·莫瑞·亞伯拉罕]]演出。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.broadwayworld.com/off-broadway/article/F-Murray-Abraham-Featured-in-YOU-CANT-TAKE-IT-WITH-YOU-Reading-28-20100207 |title = F. Murray Abraham Featured in YOU CAN'T TAKE IT WITH YOU Reading, 2/8 |date = 2010-02-08 |publisher = BroadwayWorld |language = en |accessdate = 2018-04-17 |archive-date = 2018-04-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180418031916/https://www.broadwayworld.com/off-broadway/article/F-Murray-Abraham-Featured-in-YOU-CANT-TAKE-IT-WITH-YOU-Reading-28-20100207 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

